content: To import {{importSectionName}}, enable the "<1>{{sectionName}}</1>" option first.

comment.text: This key displays a message instructing the user to enable a specific option (likely within settings) before importing a section of files or folders. It appears as a tooltip or inline message in the data import process, specifically when importing personal files. Translators should ensure "importSectionName" accurately reflects the name of the section being imported.
